    span: 'lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2',
    description:
      'A sophisticated entertaining terrace with custom stonework, integrated water features, and meticulously curated planting framing panoramic Brisbane River views.',
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    imageUrl: 'https://picsum.photos/seed/ascot-courtyard/900/1200',
    title: 'Ascot Courtyard',
    category: 'Residential Design',
    span: 'lg:row-span-2',
    description:
      'An intimate courtyard sanctuary featuring a spa, statement tree, and layered lighting creating a private urban retreat.',
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    imageUrl: 'https://picsum.photos/seed/botanical-entry/900/700',
    title: 'Botanical Entry',
    category: 'Garden Design',
    span: '',
    description:
      'An elegant arrival sequence with curated planting, premium materials, and a sculptural water feature anchoring the entry experience.',
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    imageUrl: 'https://picsum.photos/seed/pool-pavilion/1200/700',
    title: 'Pool Pavilion',
    category: 'Outdoor Architecture',
    span: 'lg:col-span-2',
    description:
      'A resort-inspired pavilion with integrated outdoor kitchen, cantilevered shade structures, and immersive landscape design for seamless entertaining.',
  },
  {
    id: 5,
    imageUrl: 'https://picsum.photos/seed/hillside-lawn/800/700',
    title: 'Hillside Retreat',
    category: 'Landscape Construction',
    span: '',
    description:
      'Terraced lawns, natural stone steps, and refined planting transforming a challenging slope into a serene, functional outdoor space.',
  },
